  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2d383c0abd126f3c.jpg?v=1782535211\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Putting together little journals of trips in a simple way might be my new favorite thing. Trying to keep things interesting while not feeling so behind on documenting my memories. This particular Palm Springs trip was taken back in February over Valentine's Day weekend! If you want to check out the video of the trip, <a href=\"https://youtu.be/-Gq3gm7AaC4\">it's up on YouTube</a> and also at the bottom of this post.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2b-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e313db8c40cf07b0.jpg?v=1782535214\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2c-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9ea35dd6d5788c24.jpg?v=1782535216\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2d-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d48f0f52f0efb043.jpg?v=1782535219\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2e-.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1c67e8903c2538da.jpg?v=1782535222\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2f-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/be682f4874465bee.jpg?v=1782535224\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2g-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8ac254313d4f07e8.jpg?v=1782535228\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2h-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6fd04a96fcf169a6.jpg?v=1782535230\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2i-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1cade2a66a52f40b.jpg?v=1782535233\"/>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2j-Palm+Springs+Traveler's+Notebook+_